questions: Is it a physical, tangible object (something you can touch)?
Is it something manufactured/made by humans (as opposed to occurring naturally)?
Is it a living thing (or part of a currently living thing)?
Is it something found on or from Earth (as opposed to being from space, like a meteor)?
Does it generate its own light/energy through nuclear fusion (like a star)?
Is it the Sun (the star at the center of our solar system)?
